{"tid":159063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保良局訓練營醜聞連環爆 總監開腔反駁：年輕一代「玻璃心」","createTime":"2017-03-16T16:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T06:42:28.000Z","uid":1925,"like":272,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d0068253b68fa343d273aa52f9ca32b3d694e5b7","tid":159063,"uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:58:01.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪<br />\n依條正人渣 咁撚樣都講得出<br />\n保良局死全家落地獄啦屌你老母<br />\n成個營都係紅底 中聯辨青年組都有參與其中<br />\n營中仲有國民教育<br />\n個乜撚野活動策動主席仲要係劉肛華<br />\n(Source from王同學fb live)<br />\n屌你老母上上下下都係仆街人渣冚家剷<br />\n而家已經唔單只係虐兒同非禮兒童咁簡單<br />\n呢獲野真係要搞到佢永不超生<br />\n唔可以再比呢班冚家剷禍害香港下一代<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170317&amp;guid=56438854&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170317%26guid%3D56438854%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=1Biu5Jcu4NfhTOeMSm0obhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=77bb9cd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170317%26guid%3D56438854%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=25a1f4b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170317&amp;guid=56438854&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"9164c40dd1da8d15acd5666a82632490d24f2686","tid":159063,"uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f60dd13da4cc49e1933f7d76b5f42fbba17a2a4","tid":159063,"uid":1925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T17:01:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06028eef05958f7c5ead4ddd51558a9107102348","tid":159063,"uid":14797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T17:01:57.000Z","msg":"咁叻咪叫你屋企人扮狗爬、食住泥上報回應囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" 